title: Commando Cody: Sky Marshal of the Universe

sources.title: Commando Cody: Sky Marshal of the Universe (1953) Marathon TV Series chapters 1-12
sources.description:
Dangerous climate changes are ravaging Earth and the U.S. government requests an investigation by masked super-scientist Commando Cody. He discovers that the disasters are being caused by space-alien forces from unknown planetary origins.

Stars: Judd Holdren, Aline Towne, Gregory Gaye

00:00 Chapter 1- Enemies of the Universe
29:48 Chapter 2- Atomic Peril
58:22 Chapter 3- Cosmic Vengeance
1:26:55 Chapter 4- Nightmare Typhoon
1:55:30 Chapter 5- War of the Space Giants
2:24:06 Chapter 6- Destroyers of the Sun
2:52:40 Chapter 7- Robot Monster from Mars
3:21:15 Chapter 8- The Hydrogen Hurricane
3:49:48 Chapter 9- Solar Sky Raiders
4:18:22 Chapter 10- S.O.S. Ice Age
4:46:57 Chapter 11- Lost in Outer Space
5:15:33 Chapter 12- Captives of the Zero Hour
